'''Akaswar''' di [[tusnakt]] d afrun i d-ittmagen seg usiweṭ n wagazen n [[tameknut|temkunt]] tumdilt s [[agaz (tanzeggit)|wagaz]] ur ten-ṭṭafar ara, tameknut tettwasemma '''azlem awehhay''' ma d agaz yettwassmma '''ixef n ukaswar''', ma yella d yal [[amaɣad (tusnakt)|amaɣad]] yessawaṭ-it gar n uzlem awehhay d yixef n ukaswar yettusemma '''amsuneɣ n ukawsar'''. Dɣa akawsar yettwassen daɣen d afrun i d-yettmagen seg tuzzya n [[taɣussi|akeṛdis aserman n tɣemrin]] ɣef kra n [[Ageddis|ugeddis]] n [[tiɣmert taɣadant|teɣmert taɣadant]] tuzzya tummidt.<br>

Mi ara ad yili uzlem awehhay d [[tawinest]], ittusemmay ukawsar d '''akawsar uwnis'''. W mi ara ad ilin yakk issunɣen mgadan deg [[teɣzi]] yettusemmay '''akawsar uwnis aɣadan'''. Ma yella negzem akawsar uwnis aɣadan s [[agni (tanzeggit)|wugni]] war ixef, agezzum i d-innulfan ad yettwassmma [[uzmig]]. Ma d '''Teflel n ukawsar''' d [[amaɣad (tusnakt)|umaɣad]] aratak seg yixef ɣer uzadur.

